<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Nice thing about casters is that you rarely get hit, so your armor doesnt degrade like tank armor does.  Therefore you can wear armor significantly higher than your level w/o destroying it.  Although you won't get the full benefit from it right away, your AF will generally be maxed out for your level (cap) & will go up each level until the armor goes yellow/blue.<P>The stuff in Barrows is fairly common & isnt usually too expensive (Risen (af37) & Delusional Power (af42) items).<P>--------------------<P>Mezmo - Sorcerer<BR>Albion - Palomides
