Sorcerors are the Salvation Army darlings of Albion. There is TONS of good stuff out there that others have no real need for. They find it all the time and usually are very generous about handing it down to us.<P>Every Sorceror I have ever played, even under a completely anonymous name has been given Netherworldly robes by level 15. Many items do not have the best armor stats, but the bonuses are nice. I gladly take those hand me downs, even if they are purple to me, because we normally encounter melee far less than almost ANY other class in the game.<P>No need to beg as a Sorceror, seems we just happen to be in the right place at the right time quite frequently....<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...
